with you one of my favorite foods it's for
homemade pizza and I don't know what it is

00:00:18.869 --> 00:00:24.470
about homemade pizza that just calls to me
maybe it's my infatuation with dough and watching

00:00:24.470 --> 00:00:30.119
it grow or pressing it between my palms or
